    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在《Starship Fighters》中驾驶你的星际飞船，一款真实的太空战斗模拟器。参与激烈的战斗，探索浩瀚的银河系，并使用强大的武器库在充满敌人的宇宙中释放毁灭！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/34096036364cb288db26af8b86e412a3.poster.avif?t=1772360408\" width=602 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/34096036364cb288db26af8b86e412a3.webm?t=1772360408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/34096036364cb288db26af8b86e412a3.mp4?t=1772360408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于《Starship Fighters》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Starship Fighters》将玩家带入充满刺激的太空战斗，横跨辽阔的宇宙。作为一名星际飞船的驾驶员，执行考验你的战斗技能和战略的紧张任务。自定义各种星际飞船，每艘飞船都配备强大的武器，适用于从空战到大规模战斗的多种场景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/d7236f5c5abbdc3549cd2c6882fca8c3.poster.avif?t=1772360408\" width=604 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/d7236f5c5abbdc3549cd2c6882fca8c3.webm?t=1772360408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/d7236f5c5abbdc3549cd2c6882fca8c3.mp4?t=1772360408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个详细的银河系，拥有多样的环境，从小行星带到外星行星，每个环境都带来独特的战术挑战。参与高速追击，巧妙超越敌人，释放强力攻击统治宇宙。凭借沉浸式的3D视觉效果和第一人称视角动作，《Starship Fighters》提供了具有无限可重玩性的模式，在每一场战斗中都带来激烈且充满肾上腺素的动作体验。</p>",
